Class Effect

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.observer.Observable

Direct Known Subclasses:
EffectDecorator, SimpleEffect 
public abstract class Effect
extends Observable
Abstract class used to implement the Decorator Pattern for the effects.
